# Consistency (ACID / MSA)

Full model: [`docs/CONSISTENCY.md`](../../docs/CONSISTENCY.md).

## Hard rules

- **Never** call cross-service `I*Client` HTTP inside `ExecuteInTransactionAsync`. Persist (or soft-delete) locally first; remotes after commit; create flows compensate with logged cleanup.
- **Deletes** are remote-first (idempotent remote cleanup), then local delete.
- **Durable side effects** (Redis Streams / pub/sub) for Media upload and Chat message create go through the **transactional outbox**, not naked post-commit enqueue.
- Internal detach/delete endpoints must stay **idempotent**.

Do not introduce distributed 2PC.
